 010100000000000000000000400000000000000040 | Mon Jan 03 00:00:00 2000 PST | {[Cbuffer(POINT(3 3),0.5)@Mon Jan 03 00:00:00 2000 PST, Cbuffer(POINT(4 4),0.5)@Tue Jan 04 00:00:00 2000 PST)}
 010100000000000000000010400000000000001040 | Mon Jan 03 00:00:00 2000 PST | {[Cbuffer(POINT(4 4),0.5)@Tue Jan 04 00:00:00 2000 PST, Cbuffer(POINT(5 5),0.5)@Wed Jan 05 00:00:00 2000 PST)}
